  "prompt": "How do I stop my Jamster subscription from charging me money?",
  "response": "To stop a Jamster subscription, you can try the following steps:\n\n1. Contact Jamster customer support directly:\n- Email or phone support\n- Visit their website and look for cancellation instructions\n\n2. Contact your mobile carrier:\n- Ask them to block or cancel the Jamster subscription\n- Request they stop premium SMS charges\n\n3. Text STOP to the Jamster short code that sends you messages\n\n4. If you're being charged through your phone bill, contact your phone provider to block premium SMS services\n\n5. Check your phone's settings to block or disable premium content subscriptions\n\nThe specific steps might vary depending on your country and mobile carrier, so it's best to contact Jamster or your carrier directly for precise instructions.",
